%% Sequence diagram for booking flow
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant C as MovieController
    participant DB as Database
    participant Q as Queue
    participant Mail as MailService

    U->>F: fill booking form and submit
    F->>C: POST /save-ticket
    C->>DB: create Booking, create Tickets
    C->>Q: dispatch SendTicketEmail job
    Q->>Mail: send email with ticket + QR
    Mail-->>U: deliver email with ticket
    C-->>F: return success / redirect to /my-tickets
